{"tid":1797193,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社區組織協會禮賓府請願 促用單程證餘額讓單親中國母來港","createTime":"2019-12-25T08:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T11:41:57.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3141b302a2051efdeca75a15d4ccc884a0792fe9","tid":1797193,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T08:24:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2814160821980400/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2814160821980400%2F&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=6a77e663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2814160821980400/</a><br />\n<br />\n【社區組織協會禮賓府請願 促用單程證餘額讓單親中國母來港】<br />\n<br />\n繼去年聖誕日之後，香港社區組織協會今日（12月25日）又有行動，與30名兩地分隔的中國單親婦人及在港子女，到禮賓府請願，要求政府妥善運用過剩單程證名額，協助單親家庭團聚。<br />\n<br />\n參與請願人士高舉標語，上面寫上「單程名額有剩，應給單親家庭」、「家庭慘分隔，聖誕無歡樂，媽媽無單程，孩子難脫貧」等標語。及後警方派出代表，接過給予特首林鄭月娥的請願信。<br />\n<br />\n社區組織協會幹事施麗珊表示，現時單程證名額有剩，提出將名額給予單親母親，讓她們來港照顧小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-25-2019/58570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-25-2019%2F58570&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=90813fe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/12-25-2019/58570</a><br />\n<br />\n#社區組織協會 #施麗珊 #單程證<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=3e61be9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=1caa0f96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">